Discover ITP's Versa Cross, the tire that offers exceptional performance and unrivaled handling on compact surfaces. Specially designed for high-powered UTVs (all-terrain utility vehicles) and SxS (side-by-side), this tire is ready to take on any challenge.

The Versa Cross is equipped with an optimized rim protector that ensures rim flange protection, even on stylish aftermarket rims. With its "Tough Tread" rubber compound, this tire provides superior protection against cuts, chips and tread wear.
The Versa Cross's reinforced belts provide increased traction and unmatched puncture resistance. With its 8-ply radial construction, this tire is designed to withstand heavy loads and demanding terrain.
Get ready for a superior off-road experience with the ITP Versa Cross. Choose performance, reliability and American quality for your off-road adventures.
Please note that the Versa Cross is certified to comply with FMVSS No. 119 for limited highway use. This means that it is suitable for road use within certain specific limits.
